# 14. Out of Scope for Phase 0.6

This document defines the API contract only, in written form. It explicitly does **not** define or produce:

- No Backend code
- No Controllers
- No Services
- No DTOs
- No Entities
- No NestJS implementation
- No Prisma implementation
- No Database queries
- No Authentication implementation
- No Frontend integration

Any of the above will be introduced only in their designated future phase, implemented using the technology stack locked in Phase 0.3 and the data model locked in Phase 0.5, and must faithfully implement — never contradict — the contracts defined in this document.

